  "title": "Administration & Accounts",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company Overview</strong></p><p>Hana Motors Pte Ltd Rent's & Lease Passenger Cars & Commercial Goods Vehicles. We Also Import Cars Directly From United Kingdom, Japan & Australia. We Do Retail & Wholesale. We Provide One Stop Solution To Our Clients. Financing / Insurance / Motor Brokerage.</p><p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will support daily administrative operations and assist with invoicing and account reconciliation using XERO software. You will help maintain vehicle leasing records and support compliance tasks under guidance and training.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform daily administrative tasks to maintain smooth and efficient office operations</li><li>Prepare and reconcile invoices and accounts using XERO software to ensure accurate financial records</li><li>Assist the company accountant in filing quarterly GST returns to maintain tax compliance</li><li>Update and maintain leasing vehicle stock records to reflect current inventory status accurately</li><li>Manage updates for road tax, vehicle inspections, and insurance renewals to ensure all vehicles comply with regulations</li><li>Submit offence details related to hirers to relevant agencies to support legal compliance</li><li>Collaborate with team members and follow guidance and training to perform duties effectively</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Hold a Class 3A driver’s licence (advantageous but not required)</li><li>Use Microsoft Office applications proficiently to support administrative tasks</li><li>Communicate fluently in English to ensure clear understanding and coordination</li><li>Work independently to complete assigned tasks efficiently</li></ul>",
